name: Lumpy the Gnome
description: Lumpy is just capable enough to move logs from one location to another.
autoCollectMessage: Lumpy carrys off $ logs, stumbling the entire way.

name: Dumpy the Gnome
description: Dumpy is more than capable enough to move logs from one location to another.

name: Grumpy the Gnome
description: Grumpy will move logs from one location to another, but he won't be happy about it.
autoCollectMessage: Grumpy mutters to himself while he takes $ logs to the bank.

name: Slumpy the Gnome
description: Slumpy is quite quick at carrying logs. It's a shame you can't do anything about his posture.
autoCollectMessage: Slumpy drags $ logs away to the bank.

name: Rumpy the Gnome
description: Rumpy has a butt-chin which has always encouraged him to move very quickly so as to never be seen.
autoCollectMessage: Rumpy scurries off with $ logs and quickly returns, hiding behind a large boulder.

name: Jumpy the Gnome
description: Jumpy is full of energy and loves to move logs between locations.
autoCollectMessage: Jumpy maneuvers the $ logs to the bank in the most uncomfortable way.

name: Thurgood the Dwarf

name: Badthur the Dwarf
description: Badthur is probably overqualified for the job.

name: Tholdbur the Dwarf
description: Tholdbur takes pride in his ability to carry ores from the mine to the bank.

name: Dwarny the Dwarf
